                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 422.11G93/816.</note>
                        <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Quito</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-10-21T15:00:00-05:14">
                                    <hi rend="italic">October 21, 1915—3 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>My telegram of October 20, 5 p.m. Negotiations mentioned were solicited
                            by Ecuadorian officials within forty-eight hours after note was
                            presented.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Hartman</hi>.</signed>
                        </closer>
